trans-unit.source: Contains the settings for the supported versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Contém as configurações para as versões com suporte do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: There are currently two versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol supported by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
trans-unit.target: Atualmente, há duas versões do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging suportados pelo [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 e WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.

trans-unit.source: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 é retornado por <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A>e WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 é retornado por <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the default version of WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a versão padrão do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the default version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Derivado de uma instância de <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> que representa a versão padrão do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: Gets version 1.1 of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a versão 1.1 do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 version.
trans-unit.target: Derivado de uma instância de <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> que representa a versão do WS-ReliableMessaging1.1.

trans-unit.source: Gets the February 2005 version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a versão de fevereiro de 2005 do protocolo WS-ReliableMessaging.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"></xref> that represents the WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 version.
trans-unit.target: Derivado de uma instância de <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion"> </xref> que representa a versão do WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
